wikipedia_page.main: Major General Sir Evelyn John Webb-Carter  (born 30 January 1946) is a retired senior British Army officer. He was the last 'Colonel of the Regiment' of the Duke of Wellington's Regiment (West Riding) (1999–2006), before their amalgamation into the Yorkshire Regiment, 3rd Battalion (Duke of Wellington's).

response: * Lieutenant Colonel Evelyn John Webb-Carter, Grenadier Guards.
